title: His Estranged Brother Ambushed Him At The Worst Possible Time!
description:
He hasn't spoken to your brother in over a year. You have a free house to use for vacation with your family. You're looking forward to having a peaceful week, but then things take a turn.
You get ambushed by your brother who you haven't spoken to in years! He shows up with his family to stay with you without warning. So what do you do?
It happened to someone Kristin knows, and today she's sharing the story with us.
